==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪtə(r)|-aɪtə(r)]]

===Adjective===
'''lighter'''

# The {{compar}} of [[light]].
#: ''I prefer a '''lighter''' shade of pink.''
#: ''What happened?  You look 10 lbs. '''lighter'''!''
#: ''I wish I'd thrown a '''lighter''' punch; he's out cold.''

===Noun===
[[Image:White_lighter_with_flame.JPG|thumb|right|A lighter (sense 1)]]
{{en-noun}}

# A small, reusable, [[handheld]] device for creating [[fire]].
#: ''Cigarette in mouth, he clutched his pockets in search of a '''lighter'''.''
# {{archaic}}: A flat-bottomed [[boat]] for carrying heavy loads across short distances (especially for [[canal]]s or for loading or unloading larger boats).

